{"url":"http://www.uokuni-s.co.jp/","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ja\">\n\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"「おいしい」のその先の価値を創りたい。魚国総本社は給食事業を通じ、食にまつわるあらゆるビジネスから人のカラダとココロの健康を育みます。\">\n    <title>おいしいをもっと　すこやかをずっと｜株式会社魚国総本社</title>\n\n    <link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/assets/images/common/favicon.ico\">\n\n    <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n    <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700&display=swap\">\n\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/assets/css/style.css\">\n\n    <!-- Google Tag Manager -->\n    <script>(function(w,d,s,l,i){w[l]=w[l]||[];w[l].push({'gtm.start':\n    new Date().getTime(),event:'gtm.js'});var f=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],\n    j=d.createElement(s),dl=l!='dataLayer'?'&l='+l:'';j.async=true;j.src=\n    'https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtm.js?id='+i+dl;f.parentNode.insertBefore(j,f);\n    })(window,document,'script','dataLayer','GTM-K98Q7BWW');</script>\n    <!-- End Google Tag Manager -->\n  </head>\n\n  <body>\n    <!-- Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->\n    <noscript><iframe src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-K98Q7BWW\"\n    height=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"display:none;visibility:hidden\"></iframe></noscript>\n    <!-- End Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->\n\n    <div class=\"l-wrapper\">\n      <header class=\"l-header\"></header>\n\n      <div class=\"p-hero\">\n        <h1 class=\"p-hero__ttl\">仕事に誇りを持ち、いつも笑顔で元気に</h1>\n        <div class=\"p-hero__block\">\n          <video class=\"p-hero__movie\" src=\"/assets/images/top/hero_movie.mp4\" autoplay playsinline loop muted preload=\"auto\"></video>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <main class=\"l-main l-main--top p-root\">\n\n        <section class=\"l-main__sec l-main__sec--full p-service__root\">\n          <div class=\"l-sec--wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"c-cards c-cards__v1 c-cards__v1--3column p-service__cards\">\n              <div class=\"c-card c-card__v1 c-card__v1--3column c-card__head\">\n                <h2 class=\"c-card__ttl\">\n                  <span class=\"c-card__ttl--cap\">Service</span>\n                  事業概要\n                </h2>\n                <p class=\"c-card__txt\">「おいしい」のその先へ。<br>食にまつわるあらゆるビジネスから<br class=\"u-d-pc-none\">人のカラダとココロの健康を育みます。</p>\n                <div class=\"c-card__btn\"><a href=\"/service/\" class=\"c-btn c-btn__v1 c-btn--red\"><span class=\"c-btn__link c-btn__link--white c-btn__arrow c-btn__arrow--white\">一覧はこちら</span></a></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"c-card c-card__v1 c-card__v1--3column\">\n                <a href=\"/service/business.html\" class=\"c-card__link\">\n                  <div class=\"c-card__thumb\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/service_thumb01_pc.jpg\" alt=\"社内食堂（オフィス・工場）\" class=\"js-image-switch\"></div>\n                  <div class=\"c-card__block\">\n                    <h3 class=\"c-card__ttl c-card__ttl--arrow\">社内食堂<br class=\"u-d-pc-none\">（オフィス・工場）</h3>\n                    <p class=\"c-card__txt\">ウェルビーイングの観点で食堂を運営し、<br class=\"u-d-sp-none\">従業員の「健康」と「幸せ」を創造。</p>\n                  </div>\n                </a>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"c-card c-card__v1 c-card__v1--3column\">\n                <a href=\"/service/kids.html\" class=\"c-card__link\">\n                  <div class=\"c-card__thumb\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/service_thumb02_pc.jpg\" alt=\"保育園・認定こども園・幼稚園\" class=\"js-image-switch\"></div>\n                  <div class=\"c-card__block\">\n                    <h3 class=\"c-card__ttl c-card__ttl--arrow\">保育園・認定こども園・<br class=\"u-d-pc-none\">幼稚園</h3>\n                    <p class=\"c-card__txt\">「食べることって楽しい！」から子どもたちの発達過程をサポート。</p>\n                  </div>\n                </a>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"c-card c-card__v1 c-card__v1--3column\">\n                <a href=\"/service/school.html\" class=\"c-card__link\">\n                  <div class=\"c-card__thumb\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/service_thumb03_pc.jpg\" alt=\"学校給食・給食センター\" class=\"js-image-switch\"></div>\n                  <div class=\"c-card__block\">\n                    <h3 class=\"c-card__ttl c-card__ttl--arrow\">学校給食・給食センター</h3>\n                    <p class=\"c-card__txt\">学校給食を「教育」のひとつと捉え自治体と連携しながらバックアップ。</p>\n                  </div>\n                </a>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"c-card c-card__v1 c-card__v1--3column\">\n                <a href=\"/service/hospital.html\" class=\"c-card__link\">\n                  <div class=\"c-card__thumb\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/service_thumb04_pc.jpg\" alt=\"病院（患者給食・職員食）\" class=\"js-image-switch\"></div>\n                  <div class=\"c-card__block\">\n                    <h3 class=\"c-card__ttl c-card__ttl--arrow\">病院（患者給食・職員食）</h3>\n                    <p class=\"c-card__txt\">生きる希望や喜びにつながる食事、患者さまの励みになる病院食を。</p>\n                  </div>\n                </a>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"c-card c-card__v1 c-card__v1--3column\">\n                <a href=\"/service/senior.html\" class=\"c-card__link\">\n                  <div class=\"c-card__thumb\"><img src=\"/assets/images/top/service_thumb05_pc.jpg\" alt=\"介護施設・福祉施設\" class=\"js-image-switch\"></div>\n                  <div class=\"c-card__block\">\n                    <h3 class=\"c-card__ttl c-card__ttl--arrow\">介護施設・福祉施設</h3>\n                    <p class=\"c-card__txt\">“食”からQOL（生活の質）を高め、利用者様の人生をもっと豊かに。</p>\n                  </div>\n                </a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"l-main__sec l-main__sec--full p-restaurant__root\">\n          <div class=\"l-sec--wrapper p-restaurant__wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"p-restaurant__img01\">\n              <img src=\"/assets/images/top/service_restaurant_img01_pc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"js-image-switch\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"p-restaurant__panel\">\n              <h2 class=\"p-restaurant__ttl\">外食事業<span>レストラン、料亭の運営によるおもてなし</span></h2>\n              <div class=\"p-restaurant__img02\">\n                <img src=\"/assets/images/top/service_restaurant_img02_pc.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"js-image-switch\">\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"p-restaurant__btn\">\n                <a href=\"/service/restaurant.html\" class=\"c-btn c-btn__v1 c-btn--red\">\n                  <span class=\"c-btn__link c-btn__link--white c-btn__arrow c-btn__arrow--white\">詳しくはこちら</span>\n                </a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"l-main__sec l-main__sec--full p-message__root\">\n          <div class=\"p-message__root-content\">\n            <div class=\"p-message__root-detail-wrap\">\n              <div class=\"p-message__root-detail\">\n                <h2 class=\"p-message__root-ttl\">\n                  <span class=\"p-message__root-ttl--cap\">Message</span>\n                  私たちがお届けするもの\n                </h2>\n                <p class=\"p-message__root-lead\">\n                  365日、いつも自然とみんなのそばに寄り添うもの。<br>そんなおいしくて健康的な食事をこれからもずっとお届けしていくために。\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"p-message__root-btn u-d-sp-none\">\n                  <a href=\"/message/\" class=\"c-btn c-btn__v1 c-btn--red\">\n                    <span class=\"c-btn__link c-btn__link--white c-btn__arrow c-btn__arrow--white\">詳しくはこちら</span>\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n                <ul class=\"p-message__root-items\">\n                  <li class=\"p-message__root-item\">\n                    <a href=\"/message/health.html\" class=\"p-message__root-link\">\n                      <div class=\"p-message__root-icon\">\n                        <img src=\"/assets/images/top/message_icon01.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"js-image-switch\">\n                      </div>\n                      <p class=\"p-message__root-text\">健康の創造</p>\n                    </a>\n                  </li>\n                  <li class=\"p-message__root-item\">\n                    <a href=\"/message/safety.html\" class=\"p-message__root-link\">\n                      <div class=\"p-message__root-icon\">\n                        <img src=\"/assets/images/top/message_icon02.png\" alt=\"\">\n                      </div>\n                      <p class=\"p-message__root-text\">徹底した衛生管理、安全管理、<br class=\"u-d-none u-d-sp-block\">感染症対策</p>\n                    </a>\n                  </li>\n                  <li class=\"p-message__root-item\">\n                    <a href=\"/message/emergency.html\" class=\"p-message__root-link\">\n                      <div class=\"p-message__root-icon\">\n                        <img src=\"/assets/images/top/message_icon03.png\" alt=\"\">\n                      </div>\n                      <p class=\"p-message__root-text\">災害時などのフレキシブルな対応</p>\n                    </a>\n                  </li>\n                  <li class=\"p-message__root-item\">\n                    <a href=\"/message/sdgs.html\" class=\"p-message__root-link\">\n                      <div class=\"p-message__root-icon\">\n                        <img src=\"/assets/images/top/message_icon04.png\" alt=\"\">\n                      </div>\n                      <p class=\"p-message__root-text\">食堂を起点としたお客様の<br><span class=\"text_palt\">「SDGs推進」「ESG経営に貢献」</span></p>\n                    </a>\n                  </li>\n                </ul>\n                <div class=\"p-message__root-btn u-d-none u-d-sp-block\">\n                  <a href=\"/message/\" class=\"c-btn c-btn__v1 c-btn--red\">\n                    <span class=\"c-btn__link c-btn__link--white c-btn__arrow c-btn__arrow--white\">詳しくはこちら</span>\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"p-message__root-img\"></div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"l-main__sec l-main__sec--full p-concept__root\">\n          <div class=\"p-concept__content\">\n            <div class=\"p-concept__detail-wrap\">\n              <div class=\"p-concept__detail\">\n                <h2 class=\"p-concept__ttl\">\n                  <span class=\"p-concept__ttl--cap\">Concept</span>\n                  魚国総本社の事業コンセプト\n                </h2>\n                <p class=\"p-concept__lead\">\n                  私たちは健康創造企業として、お客様それぞれのニーズに応え、従業員が働きがいを感じられる職場をつくり、社会に貢献できる企業をめざしています。<br>\n                  そして“食”を通じて社会に貢献できることを、お客様も従業員もともに喜び合えるような温かいHuman Companyでありたいと願っています。\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"p-concept__btn u-d-sp-none\">\n                  <a href=\"/corporate/concept.html\" class=\"c-btn c-btn__v1 c-btn--red\">\n                    <span class=\"c-btn__link c-btn__link--white c-btn__arrow c-btn__arrow--white\">詳しくはこちら</span>\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n                <ul class=\"p-concept__items\">\n                  <li class=\"p-concept__item\">\n                    <div class=\"p-concept__icon\">\n                      <img src=\"/assets/images/top/concept_icon01.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"js-image-switch\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"p-concept__text-wrap\">\n                      <p class=\"p-concept__text\">【 CS  お客様満足 】</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </li>\n                  <li class=\"p-concept__item\">\n                    <div class=\"p-concept__icon\">\n                      <img src=\"/assets/images/top/concept_icon02.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"js-image-switch\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"p-concept__text-wrap\">\n                      <p class=\"p-concept__text\">【 ES  従業員満足 】</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </li>\n                  <li class=\"p-concept__item\">\n                    <div class=\"p-concept__icon\">\n                      <img src=\"/assets/images/top/concept_icon03.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"js-image-switch\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"p-concept__text-wrap\">\n                      <p class=\"p-concept__text\">【 SS  社会的満足 】</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </li>\n                </ul>\n                <div class=\"p-concept__btn u-d-none u-d-sp-block\">\n                  <a href=\"/concept/\" class=\"c-btn c-btn__v1 c-btn--red\">\n                    <span class=\"c-btn__link c-btn__link--white c-btn__arrow c-btn__arrow--white\">詳しくはこちら</span>\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"p-concept__img\"></div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"l-main__sec l-main__sec--full p-recruit__root\">\n          <div class=\"l-sec--wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"p-recruit__panel\">\n              <h2 class=\"p-recruit__ttl\">\n                <span class=\"p-recruit__ttl--cap\">Recruit</span>\n                採用情報\n              </h2>\n              <p class=\"p-recruit__txt\">全国の活躍フィールド＆充実の人財教育を<br class=\"u-d-pc-none\">活かし<br class=\"u-d-block u-d-sp-none\">自分らしい働き方とキャリアを<br class=\"u-d-none u-d-sp-block\">デザインしてください。</p>\n              <div class=\"p-recruit__btn\">\n                <a href=\"/recruit/\" class=\"c-btn c-btn__v1 c-btn--red\">\n                  <span class=\"c-btn__link c-btn__link--white c-btn__arrow c-btn__arrow--white\">詳しくはこちら</span>\n                </a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"l-main__sec l-main__sec--full p-training__root\">\n          <div class=\"l-sec--wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"p-training__panel\">\n              <h2 class=\"p-training__ttl\">\n                <span class=\"p-training__ttl--cap\">Training</span>\n                人財育成\n              </h2>\n              <p class=\"p-training__txt\">\n                おいしくて楽しい食事は、人がつくるもの。<br>\n                だからこそ教育に力を注いでいます。\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"p-training__btn\">\n                <a href=\"/corporate/training.html\" class=\"c-btn c-btn__v1 c-btn--red\">\n                  <span class=\"c-btn__link c-btn__link--white c-btn__arrow c-btn__arrow--white\">詳しくはこちら</span>\n                </a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"l-main__sec l-main__sec--full p-news__root\">\n          <div class=\"l-sec--wrapper p-news__block\">\n            <h2 class=\"p-news__ttl\">\n              <span class=\"p-news__ttl--cap\">News</span>\n              お知らせ\n            </h2>\n            <dl class=\"p-news__def\">\n              <div>\n                <dt class=\"p-news__date\">2026.06.01</dt>\n                <dd class=\"p-news__lede\"><a href=\"/assets/pdf/20260601.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">弊社サポート先　大阪ブルテオン様が「2025-26　SVリーグ」で優勝しました。</a></dd>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <dt class=\"p-news__date\">2026.05.22</dt>\n                <dd class=\"p-news__lede\"><a href=\"/assets/pdf/20260522-01.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">富山テレビ放送にて、弊社の取引先であるアイシン軽金属株式会社様・十全化学株式会社様の社員食堂が紹介されました。</a></dd>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <dt class=\"p-news__date\">2026.05.22</dt>\n                <dd class=\"p-news__lede\"><a href=\"/assets/pdf/20260522-02.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">NHK 京都にて、弊社の取引先である吉忠株式会社様の社員食堂が紹介されました。</a></dd>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <dt class=\"p-news__date\">2026.05.22</dt>\n                <dd class=\"p-news__lede\"><a href=\"/assets/pdf/20260522-03.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">RBC 琉球放送ネットニュースにて、 弊社の取引先である那覇市立識名小学校給食事業所が紹介されました。</a></dd>\n              </div>\n              <d